  m_Name: GSWTIAH_Module_2_Q7
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: "In cyber resilience the business priority is to support \u201Ccontinuous
    availability\u201D, the expectation is of always-on systems with zero downtime,
    and at the same time, our systems are more heterogeneous than ever. Which technologies
    will be critical to solving this expectation and complexity?"
  answers:
  - Artificial Intelligence
  - Predictive systems
  - Orchestration as part of a software-defined resiliency story
  - All of the above
  maxSelections: 1
